MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2006-2182. State of Ohio ex rel. Dann v. Marshall.

Scioto App. No. 05CA3004, 2006-Ohio-5357. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Scioto County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
